If Charlotte is to overturn 500 years of history, she needs more evidence.

00:26:00.160 --> 00:26:05.920
At the Hull site she has found signs of the disease in more than half the skeletons.

00:26:06.470 --> 00:26:10.540
But it's true to say that this is the very reason that Hull is so important.

00:26:13.400 --> 00:26:18.699
Syphilis has not been fun distributed across medieval Europe, like it seems to be in America.

