Or even from the 1500s. I mean, this is such an important issue within the history of medicine

00:33:41.640 --> 00:33:48.580
within the history of disease, within the history of the world, that it seems to me that all of this evidence would be there by now.

00:33:49.780 --> 00:33:55.680
For George, more classic cases of syphilis would have to be unearthed in the northeast of England and elsewhere

00:33:56.110 --> 00:33:59.010
before he would agree to give up the Columbus theory.

