00:36:03.480 --> 00:36:10.240
In effect, the whole of the Columbus theory rested on four or five skeletons.

00:36:10.240 --> 00:36:14.020
And yet, still it stood, apparently unshakeable.

00:36:16.860 --> 00:36:25.140
That is, until another skeleton was found with the distinctive teeth to finally shatter this distorted view of history.

00:36:26.420 --> 00:36:39.000
A skeleton found not in America, nor in medieval Europe, but from a town that flourished 2,000 years before the death of skeleton 1216.

00:36:52.160 --> 00:36:57.580
