When I told him that I have two examples of the teeth change accrue as it is found in congenital syphilis,

00:38:49.540 --> 00:38:58.020
Maciej was very happy, because finally we had the picture of syphilis coming together.

00:38:58.560 --> 00:39:05.360
The Hennebergs knew that if they were right, the presence of syphilis in Europe had nothing to do with Columbus.

00:39:10.620 --> 00:39:13.720
But if it had been in Europe since classical times,

00:39:13.720 --> 00:39:18.600
then they should also find evidence of the disease at their other archaeological site.

00:39:19.000 --> 00:39:21.440
The ancient Roman remains at Pompeii.

00:39:26.200 --> 00:39:30.080
